>\n-百德浸信會青少青區<br />\n-觀潮浸信會 THE FLOW<br />\n（歡迎更多加入的教會及單位）<br />\n<br />\n緊急招募以下四種人：<br />\n<br />\n1.DSE考試戰略研究員<br />\n（要求：DSE過來人（最低要求其中一科5*)<br />\n網上登記報名連結如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/LnJarDR2a4NjGTDk6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FLnJarDR2a4NjGTDk6&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=4d49b3a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/LnJarDR2a4NjGTDk6</a><br />\n<br />\n2.DSE Direct Support Group<br />\nA.校車家長 Group (負責接送考生)<br />\nB.老師打氣Group (考試貼士)<br />\nC.情緒支援 Group (了解及關顧考生應試時等情緒及輔導)<br />\nD.文宣媒體Group  (在社交媒體上，公佈相關資料等)<br />\nE.懶人包Group (提提考生須知)<br />\nF.策略孵化箱Group  (再思再想，看看DSE後的跟進)<br />\nG.分區抖氣位Group  (籌劃實體放鬆活動）<br />\n網上登記報名連結如下： <br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/z8JF58wcexzF2M5p9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fz8JF58wcexzF2M5p9&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=d785c7e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/z8JF58wcexzF2M5p9</a><br />\n<br />\n3.DSE 白金聯盟（奉獻金主）<br />\n網上登記報名連結如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/dEnZmb4uVGgp4WVZ7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FdEnZmb4uVGgp4WVZ7&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=469f049e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/dEnZmb4uVGgp4WVZ7</a><br />\n<br />\n 4.全港應屆DSE考生<br />\n網上登記報名連結如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/p1Q8d9MJcnVtfs7j9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fp1Q8d9MJcnVtfs7j9&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=f1b6d1f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/p1Q8d9MJcnVtfs7j9</a> <br />\n<br />\n各科考試攻略網上教室採用Zoom 視像軟件，由DSE學生自行判斷報名加入，坐滿即止，每一科分三個Level:<br />\nLevel 1 ：目標合格<br />\nLevel 2  : 目標考高多一級<br />\nLevel 3 ：目標 5*<br />\n*所有Zoom課堂教學錄影會在課程完結48小時內 upload到 DSE雞精聯盟2020 youtube Channel免費重溫<br />\n<br />\n開始日期：<br />\n3月1日起，陪足您100日plus+，唔俾您孤單！<br />\n<br />\n零門檻- 任何應屆DSE考生都可以參加<br />\n零收費- 所有各科考試攻略網上教室費用全免<br />\n零風險- 無需入會被迫參加任何宗教活動<br />\n<br />\n時間無多，請用盡方法通知你認識的應屆DSE考生，並選擇招募對象連結，報名登記加盟。//"},{"pid":"26061c239e439e4f6ee01dc3bd05cea3974cf609","tid":1895404,"uid":72847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"488afeb4065c8bedd2be790b0bc027eeded5a3c3","tid":1895404,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08b107903bd9b492565e0774611efe57b8841e93","tid":1895404,"uid":72847,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T20:04:39.000Z","msg":"真 條臭西叫我去讀fd<br />\n而家double Master <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"讀咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"咩叫讀左幾耐？<br />\n中六之後唔想讀書，去左打銀行工<br />\n做左一年終於知自己中意讀咩科，就報番u<br />\n然後收左<br />\n讀u中途仲去左牛大讀一個sem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ngrad左就讀多左兩個master，一個香港一個去左英國讀<br />\n<br />\n所以想講唔好隨波逐流，聽中學d垃圾老師講，比人洗腦<br />\n唔好為讀而讀<br />\n發掘下自己到底興趣係邊先再搵書讀都唔遲"},{"pid":"cf4b9a884cd28032abb291c5ea980c5fb3c70707","tid":1895404,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26061c239e439e4f6ee01dc3bd05cea3974cf609","tid":1895404,"uid":72847,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"488afeb4065c8bedd2be790b0bc027eeded5a3c3","tid":1895404,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08b107903bd9b492565e0774611efe57b8841e93","tid":1895404,"uid":72847,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T20:04:39.000Z","msg":"真 條臭西叫我去讀fd<br />\n而家double Master <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T08:27:34.000Z","msg":"讀咗幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"咩叫讀左幾耐？<br />\n中六之後唔想讀